<ul>
<li>Get the most out of your workforce</li>
<li>Reduce your exposure to the risk of legal fines or employee tribunals</li>
<li>Concentrate on running your business</li>
</ul>
<p>We offer our services/products on either an ad hoc or service contract basis, to best fit your type of business and its requirements. All our Human Resource/Personnel solutions are tailored to your business, as every business has employment issues and requirements that are different.</p>
<p><br />All our consultants are CIPD (Chartered Institute of Personnel and Development) qualified, or an expert in their field, and have the knowledge and experience to assist with any employee problems/requirement and can often suggest solutions to your business which can save you money or make your staff more productive with little outlay.</p>
<p><br />Using our services on a contract basis is more cost effective than on an ad hoc basis, and can be for as little as 2 hours per month upwards. It is a flexible contract whereby you are able to increase or decrease your hours* and even carry over your hours to the following month.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;">*Subject to terms and conditions</span></p></td>
